---- MODULE MCDieHarder ----

(**************************************************************************)
(* The following definitions duplicate the original Die Hard problem.      *)
(**************************************************************************)

CONSTANTS Goal     \* The goal state.
    == 4

Jug      \* The capacity of the jug.
    == 3

Capacity \* The capacity of the container.
    == 5

Spec == \* The specification.
    /\ Goal = 4
    /\ \A x \in 0..Capacity : x \in DOMAIN Jug
    /\ \A x \in 0..Jug : x \in DOMAIN Capacity
    /\ \A x \in 0..Capacity : x \in DOMAIN Goal
    /\ \A x \in 0..Jug : x \in DOMAIN Goal
